                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7786" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1217</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2238 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“芯”生态，“芯”生代： 中芯集成科创板上市赋能“芯”发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Core” Ecology, “Core” Generation:  The Listing of SMIC Integrated Science and Technology Innovation Board Empowers the Development of “Core”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周蕾，张凤莲，张丽英，宋佳宁，程滨萍，刘梦琼，蒋蓉蓉，司淑娟，张乔雅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绍兴中芯集成电路制造股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科创板融资；亏损上市；研发与创新；投资价值</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Science and Technology Innovation Board financing; Listing at a loss; R&amp;D and innovation; Investment value</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了在中美贸易摩擦和芯片技术封锁的背景下，三年累计巨亏43亿的新生企业-中芯集成，成功在科创板上市的艰辛历程。阅读本案例，可以知晓处于重重困难中的中芯集成，如何挖掘自身优势，逐一破解难题，回应外界质疑，最终通过科创板上市以实现自身跨越式发展和多方共赢局面。本案例通过梳理中芯集成的上市过程，旨在引导学生熟悉和掌握科创板上市条件；了解股东财富最大化理论、利益相关者导向理论、企业创新理论等基础理论知识；学习和掌握价值投资的相关知识，并判断亏损企业是否具备投资价值；思考中芯集成科创板成功上市对自身及产业链上“芯”生态内高科技公司创新能力提升的机制。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the arduous journey of SMIC, a new enterprise with a huge loss of 4.3 billion in three years, to successfully be listed on the Science and Technology Innovation Board against the background of Sino-US trade friction and chip technology blockade. By reading this case, you can learn how SMIC, which is facing many difficulties, explores its own advantages, solves problems one by one, responds to external doubts, and finally achieves its own leapfrog development and win-win situation by listing on the Science and Technology Innovation Board. By combing through the listing process of SMIC, this case aims to guide students to become familiar with and master the conditions for listing on the Science and Technology Innovation Board; to understand basic theoretical knowledge such as shareholder wealth maximization theory, stakeholder orientation theory, and corporate innovation theory; to learn and master value investment Relevant knowledge, and determine whether loss-making enterprises have investment value; think about the mechanism by which the successful listing of SMIC&#39;s Science and Technology Innovation Board will improve the innovation capabilities of itself and high-tech companies in the &quot;core&quot; ecosystem in the industry chain.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《MBA会计学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科创板上市条件；股东利益最大化理论；利益相关者导向理论；企业生命周期理论；企业创新理论；投资价值；研发与创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
